---
title: Tarragon Pork Loin with Garlic-Kumara & Greens
description: We’ve combined these succulent pork loins with a divine tarragon sauce that’ll blow the socks off the people 'round your dinner table. The trick here is to make sure your pork isn’t overcooked – we like to leave it just ever so slightly pink in the middle to enjoy all the juicy deliciousness!
